title: to restart all sound programs
pid: 6b82e40e-8519-4f5b-946a-267266cc4d04
body: |2-
  via ChatGPT
  systemctl --user restart pipewire wireplumber
  # It suggested these but they are not found (let alone restarted).
  pipewire-media-session
  jack
  pipewire-pulse
  # Neither do these.
  jackd
  jackdbus
